  m_text: "How To Play:\n\u2022\tSelect a building \u2013 Choose the type of building
    you want to place from the building menu.\r\n\u2022\tPlace the building \u2013
    Move the building preview to the desired location and place it on the map.\r\n\u2022\tManage
    your town \u2013 Monitor your resources as buildings generate income or consume
    resources.\r\n\u2022\tIncrease your population \u2013 Build houses to increase
    the housing.\r\n\nControls:\r\n\u2022\tLeft Mouse Button: Place the selected
    building.\r\n\u2022\tRight Mouse Button: Cancel build.\n\u2022\tRight Mouse Button
    + Move Mouse: Rotate the camera.\n\u2022\tMouse scroll wheel: Zoom in/out.\n\u2022\tButton
    \u201CR\u201D + Mouse Scroll Wheel: Rotate the building.\r\n\u2022\tPoint at
    an object + Button \u201CD\u201D: Delete the object.\n\nCheats:\n\u2022\tButton
    \u201CP\u201D: Add resources.\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8b5cd8c33dcc19147a64dc7b87cbdb07, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 5915189131757618624, guid: 8b5cd8c33dcc19147a64dc7b87cbdb07, type: 2}
